  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/569db1cc1d446adf19e295d051b20e1c.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Backrooms: Escape Together is a co-op survival horror game featuring lifelike graphics, proximity voice chat and horrifying entities. You and up to 5 friends must make your way through 10 fully procedurally generated levels using what's available to you to progress deeper into the Backrooms. <br><br>Every level is a mini-adventure of its own, hosting unique gameplay, puzzles, lootable items, environments, and entities. <strong>Levels will be added constantly throughout early access as we grow the game into the best multiplayer experience to date.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/4f0dcce46172c6682b483b7527f0ec56.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything is re-generated on the fly after every level attempt. No two rooms, hallways, or encounters are the same offering unparalleled replay-ability. Each level's procedural generation algorithm is meticulously designed to capture the essence of the Backrooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/d1d31d0fd91df0d062e776911039355a.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/d1d31d0fd91df0d062e776911039355a.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/d1d31d0fd91df0d062e776911039355a.mp4?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/322e15d1b8f9314ac52efb00d10deecd.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made in Unreal Engine 5, Backrooms: Escape Together's lifelike visuals and spatialized audio work to remove every possible immersion barrier between you and the game. You will feel as if you truly are a lost wander, stuck in the Backrooms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/7486db898e6dd0b61a2b4dbdd9020be4.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/7486db898e6dd0b61a2b4dbdd9020be4.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/7486db898e6dd0b61a2b4dbdd9020be4.mp4?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/64ffa700d25065ee8489bb8ef0b0c9f6.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the Backrooms alone or team up with 5 others for a total of 6-player co-op.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy hilarious tension relieving moments as you watch your friends die from the horrors you encounter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic proximity voice chat adapts to walls, rooms, and new environments on the fly</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Host private lobbies for your friends only or join a public lobby for an adventure with a stranger</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/01b6af01bdb932388c10ec451fab6dae.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/01b6af01bdb932388c10ec451fab6dae.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/01b6af01bdb932388c10ec451fab6dae.mp4?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/acb2516b558885e8b2fef3d31e064013.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every entity, level, exit, and design decision has been based on the online lore of the Backrooms. We take lore accuracy seriously.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a team of researchers, you are tasked to explore the liminal labyrinth. However, after completing your research duties, an elevator malfunction leaves you with only 2 objectives, survival and escape.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b02d09f81640f696896f1edb70dbc612.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b02d09f81640f696896f1edb70dbc612.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b02d09f81640f696896f1edb70dbc612.mp4?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/569db1cc1d446adf19e295d051b20e1c.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Backrooms: Escape Together is a co-op survival horror game featuring lifelike graphics, proximity voice chat and horrifying entities. You and up to 5 friends must make your way through 10 fully procedurally generated levels using what's available to you to progress deeper into the Backrooms. <br><br>Every level is a mini-adventure of its own, hosting unique gameplay, puzzles, lootable items, environments, and entities. <strong>Levels will be added constantly throughout early access as we grow the game into the best multiplayer experience to date.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/4f0dcce46172c6682b483b7527f0ec56.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything is re-generated on the fly after every level attempt. No two rooms, hallways, or encounters are the same offering unparalleled replay-ability. Each level's procedural generation algorithm is meticulously designed to capture the essence of the Backrooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/d1d31d0fd91df0d062e776911039355a.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/d1d31d0fd91df0d062e776911039355a.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass