, and new environments on the fly</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Host private lobbies for your friends only or join a public lobby for an adventure with a stranger</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/01b6af01bdb932388c10ec451fab6dae.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/01b6af01bdb932388c10ec451fab6dae.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/01b6af01bdb932388c10ec451fab6dae.mp4?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/acb2516b558885e8b2fef3d31e064013.webp?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every entity, level, exit, and design decision has been based on the online lore of the Backrooms. We take lore accuracy seriously.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a team of researchers, you are tasked to explore the liminal labyrinth. However, after completing your research duties, an elevator malfunction leaves you with only 2 objectives, survival and escape.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b02d09f81640f696896f1edb70dbc612.poster.avif?t=1770684155\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b02d09f81640f696896f1edb70dbc612.webm?t=1770684155\" type=\"video/webm; codec